<Tab title="Multiple items per thread">

Computes an exclusive block-wide prefix scan using addition (+) as the scan operator. Each thread contributes an array of consecutive input elements. The value of 0 is applied as the initial value, and is assigned to \`output[0]\` in *thread*<sub>0</sub>.

<CodeBlock links={{"BlockScan": "/library/api/cub::BlockScan"}}>
\`\`\`cpp showLineNumbers={false}
