    const _Env &__env = {}
)
\`\`\`
</CodeBlock>

<Note>
If \`__ilist.size() == 0\` then no memory is allocated
</Note>

**Parameters**

<ParamField path="__ilist" type="::cuda::std::initializer_list< _Tp >">
The initializer_list being copied into the buffer.
</ParamField>

<ParamField path="__env" type="const _Env &" default="{}">
The environment used to query the memory resource.
</ParamField>

</Tab>
<Tab title="Overload 9">

