cuda::buffer<_Tp, _Properties>::buffer(
    ::cuda::stream_ref __stream,
    _Resource &&__resource,
    _Range &&__range,
    const _Env &__env = {}
)
\`\`\`
</CodeBlock>

<Note>
If \`__range.size() == 0\` then no memory is allocated.
</Note>

**Parameters**

