### HeadSegmentedReduce <Badge intent="note" minimal>inline</Badge> <Badge intent="note" minimal>nodiscard</Badge>

Computes a segmented reduction in the calling warp where segments are defined by head-flags. The reduction of each segment is returned to the first lane in that segment (which always includes *lane*<sub>0</sub>).

Supports non-commutative reduction operators

