is \`{0, 1, 2, 3, ..., 31}\` and is \`{1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, ..., 1, 0, 0, 0}\`, respectively. The corresponding output \`aggregate\` in threads 0, 4, 8, etc. will be \`3\`, \`7\`, \`11\`, etc. (and is undefined in other threads).

